short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A plugin for users to auto accept their matches on esportal

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Esportal autoaccept is a tool for players at esportal.com to auto accept their matches while they are in que for a game or waiting for users to join a gather.
